The FAA has established a procedure in
accordance with 49 U.S.C. § 44114(b) by
which private aircraft owners can request
certain personally identifiable
information, such as names and
addresses, be withheld from broad
dissemination or display on a publicly
available FAA website. The Party Names
previously found on this page are not
available at this time due to the
implementation of these changes in public
availability of information associated
with registered aircraft.
